HARMONY ELECTRON said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 46.66% to NT$268,675,000 from NT$503,696,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            268,675          503,696    
YOY%             -46.66%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,078,448        1,916,808   
YOY%             -43.74% 
=================================================================
 